{"tid":1655780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加鐵架唔使拆！TVBuddy永不落架","createTime":"2019-10-15T08:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T06:55:19.000Z","uid":17646,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4575f6d5a8d582b951250d5cdde7abe42fa2d7d8","tid":1655780,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:39:13.000Z","msg":"安置於將軍澳電視城廣播城大門外多年的無綫吉祥物TVBuddy，近期被投訴涉嫌因違規建築，屬僭建物而遭屋宇署發出清拆令。<br />\n<br />\n今日見電視城外有吊臂，但原來並非清拆TVBuddy，據知無綫已成功向屋宇署申請，只要在TVBuddy加建鐵架以作穩固，並不需要清拆，換句話說吉祥物TVBuddy將會繼續豎立在電視城外陪伴大家！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20191015/photo/bkn-20191015161147588-1015_00862_001_02p.jpg?20191015162311\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20191015%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20191015161147588-1015_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20191015162311&h=13911400&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35e6438b83922cae53fe0f594f78f37f253eecba","tid":1655780,"uid":228910,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:46:43.000Z","msg":"即係整撚到坐監咁樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235a5c1c2f4a30d5a6f68fc2891ad79e869140d3","tid":1655780,"uid":259530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:53:03.000Z","msg":"今晚開show啦，大家記得準時到<br />\n<br />\n追擊CCTVB收入來源 -  齊來支持聽晚張彥博演唱會<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1652895\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1652895</a>"},{"pid":"711a6be40c1c5776796b4e8cc5ae98a61f876958","tid":1655780,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"35e6438b83922cae53fe0f594f78f37f253eecba","tid":1655780,"uid":228910,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T08:46:43.000Z","msg":"即係整撚到坐監咁樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.